= Robotrek (SNES) - Formulas =

This page documents the game mechanics formulas in Robotrek.

== Combat Formulas ==

=== Damage Calculation ===

'''Physical Damage:'''
<pre>
Base Damage = (Power * WeaponPower) / 4
Defense = Guard / 2
Raw Damage = Base Damage - Defense
Variance = Random(-5 to +5)
Final Damage = Max(1, Raw Damage + Variance)
</pre>

'''Critical Hit:'''
<pre>
Critical Chance = (Speed / 256) * 100%
Critical Damage = Final Damage * 1.5
</pre>

'''Armor Pierce (Drill):'''
<pre>
Defense = Guard / 4  (halved)
</pre>

=== Speed and Turn Order ===

<pre>
Turn Value = 256 - Speed
Action Gauge += (Speed + 10)
Turn triggers when Action Gauge >= 256
</pre>

'''First Strike:'''
<pre>
Player First = (Player Speed > Enemy Speed + 10)
Enemy First = (Enemy Speed > Player Speed + 20)
</pre>

