== Robot Stats ==

=== Base Robot Stats ===

<pre>
Robot HP = 100 + (Player Level * 5) + Body HP Bonus
Robot EN = 50 + (Player Level * 2)
Robot Power = 10 + (Player Level / 2) + Equipment Power
Robot Guard = 10 + (Player Level / 3) + Equipment Guard
Robot Speed = 10 + (Player Level / 4) + Part Speed Modifiers
</pre>

=== Robot Part Stacking ===

<pre>
Total Power = Base Power + Head Power + Body Power + Arm Power + Leg Power
Total Guard = Base Guard + Head Guard + Body Guard + Arm Guard + Leg Guard
Total Speed = Base Speed + Head Speed + Body Speed + Arm Speed + Leg Speed
</pre>

