=== Invention Quality ===

<pre>
Quality = Sum(Material Values) + (Level / 5)
Poor: Quality < 5
Normal: 5 <= Quality < 10
Good: 10 <= Quality < 15
Excellent: Quality >= 15
</pre>

== Shop Economics ==

=== Buy/Sell Prices ===

<pre>
Sell Price = Buy Price / 2
</pre>

