* Chapter 5: All items

== Enemy Scaling ==

=== Enemy Stats by Area ===

<pre>
Enemy HP = Base HP * (1 + Area * 0.2)
Enemy Power = Base Power * (1 + Area * 0.15)
Enemy Guard = Base Guard * (1 + Area * 0.1)
</pre>

=== Drop Calculations ===

<pre>
Drop Roll = Random(0-99)
Item Dropped if Drop Roll < Drop Rate

Drop Rate Modifiers:
- Lucky Charm: +10%
- Overkill (2x damage): +5%
- First Turn Kill: +3%
</pre>

